title: 'Nx Enterprise Podcast Episode 4: Cvent Platform Architecture Panel'
slug: 'cvent-podcast-3'
authors: ['Zack DeRose']
tags: [podcast]
cover_image: /blog/images/2024-08-21/ep-4-cvent.png
