tags: [nx, release]
description: 'Nx 19.5 brings StackBlitz support, Bun and Pnpm v9 compatibility, local flaky task detection, and more.'
---

## Table of Contents

In this blog post:

- [Video Summary](#video-summary)
- [Announcing Nx Cloud Hobby Tier](#announcing-nx-cloud-hobby-tier)
